&=\frac{\text { Volume of work material removed }\left(V_{m}\right)}{\text { Volume of wheel wear }\left(V_{w}\right)} \\
200&=\frac{\text { Volume of work material removed }\left(V_{m}\right)}{\text { Volume of wheel wear }\left(V_{w}\right)}
